################# Start of all the settings

# KEY DEFINITIONS TO REMEMBER
# $mod = Set below
# Mod4 = Super key
# Mod1 = ALT key
# Control = CTRL key
# Shift = SHIFT key
# Escape = ESCAPE key
# Return = ENTER or RETURN key
# KP_Enter = Keypad Enter
# Pause = PAUSE key
# Print = PRINT key
# Tab = TAB key
# iconic font icon search: https://fontawesome.com/v5/cheatsheet

